{
  "logNo": "110154773719",
  "title": "알레르기 비염에 침치료가 효과적이라는 연구결과가 &#39;Allergy&#39;라는 국제 저널에 발표되었네요.",
  "addDate": "2012. 12. 22.",
  "categoryNo": "15",
  "parentCategoryNo": "9",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110154773719",
  "html_size": 203746,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110154773719\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110154773719\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">어른, 아이 가릴 것 없이 환절기만 되면 콧물, 재체기, 코막힘으로 고생하게 만드는게 알러지성 비염이다. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">알러지성 비염이 있는 본인이 괴로운 것 뿐 아니라, 주변인들에게도 피해를 주기 마련. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">그래서 사람을 상대해야 하는 직업인 경우 알러지성 비염을 치료하고픈 마음는 더욱 절실해진다. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">그러나 알러지성 비염은 쉽게 낫질 않는다. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">좋다는 민간요법을 다 써봐도, 알러지 약을 사서 먹어도 효과가 있는 듯 하다가 다시금 재발한다. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">이런 알러지성 비염에 침치료가 효과적이라는 연구결과가 있어 눈길을 끈다. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121222_194/isuhani_1356140087862TiuKc_JPEG/%BA%F1%BF%B0.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"230\" height=\"219\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 230px; rheight: 219px\" id=\"20121222_194/isuhani_1356140087862TiuKc_JPEG/%BA%F1%BF%B0.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BC74D7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121222_194/isuhani_1356140087862TiuKc_JPEG/%BA%F1%BF%B0.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">알레르기 비염 치료에 침치료가 효과적이라는 임상연구결과가 알레르기 관련&nbsp;권위있는 국제 학술지인 \"ALLERGY(알러지)\"지에&nbsp;실렸다.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">이번 연구는 국내연구진들에 의해 진행된 다기관 무작위대조연구이다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">238명의 환자를 대상으로 한 본 연구에서&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">1주일에 3회씩 총 4주간 치료를 받은 후 그 경과를 관찰한 결과</span></strong>,&nbsp;가짜 침(sham acupuncture)&nbsp;치료와 대기자군에 비해 진짜 침 치료가 알러지비염환자의 증상척도(TNSS, TNNSS)를 유의하게 개선시키는것이 확인되었다.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">이미 기존의 연구들(<a style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://blog.naver.com/lunarmix?Redirect=Log&amp;logNo=60132433530)%C0%BB\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.naver.com/lunarmix?Redirect=Log&amp;logNo=60132433530)을</a>&nbsp;통해서도 침 치료가 알러지 비염에 효과적인것이라는것이 밝혀진 만큼, 알러지 비염을 한의원에서 치료받으시는것은 과학적으로도 합리적인 선택이 될 것이다.</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121222_248/isuhani_1356140437564MmLwu_JPEG/imagesCAA7FZ1I.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"249\" height=\"202\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 249px; rheight: 202px\" id=\"20121222_248/isuhani_1356140437564MmLwu_JPEG/imagesCAA7FZ1I.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BC74D7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121222_248/isuhani_1356140437564MmLwu_JPEG/imagesCAA7FZ1I.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: '994268_10'; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62)\"><a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 11px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" title=\"Allergy.\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23253122#\" target=\"_blank\">Allergy.</a>&nbsp;2012 Dec 18. doi: 10.1111/all.12053. [Epub ahead of print]</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.12em; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); MARGIN: 0.37em 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); FONT-SIZE: 1.23em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">A multicenter, randomized, controlled trial testing the effects of&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 16px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;on allergic rhinitis.</h1>\r\n<div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 19px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); FONT-SIZE: 0.92em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"auths\"><a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Choi%20SM%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Choi SM</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Park%20JE%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Park JE</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Li%20SS%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Li SS</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Jung%20H%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Jung H</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Zi%20M%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Zi M</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Kim%20TH%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Kim TH</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Jung%20S%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Jung S</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Kim%20A%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Kim A</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Shin%20M%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Shin M</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Sul%20JU%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Sul JU</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Hong%20Z%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Hong Z</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Jiping%20Z%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Jiping Z</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Lee%20S%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Lee S</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Liyun%20H%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Liyun H</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Kang%20K%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Kang K</a>,&nbsp;<a style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; WORD-WRAP: break-word; COLOR: rgb(102,0,102); FONT-SIZE: 12px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed?term=Baoyan%20L%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=23253122\" target=\"_blank\">Baoyan L</a>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.09em; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); FONT-SIZE: 0.84em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"aff\">\r\n<h3 style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; POSITION: absolute; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.2857; MARGIN: 1.28em 0px 0.64em; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; WIDTH: 1px; BOTTOM: 7px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; HEIGHT: 1px; COLOR: rgb(114,65,40); FONT-SIZE: 1.07em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; OVERFLOW: hidden; BORDER-TOP: 0px; TOP: auto; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; LEFT: -10000px\" class=\"label\">Source</h3>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-TOP: 0.5em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; FONT-SIZE: 11px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\">Department of Medical Research, Korea Institute of Oriental Medicine, Daejeon, South Korea.</p></div>\r\n<div style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 17px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); MARGIN: 1.2em auto auto; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; COLOR: rgb(62,62,62); VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"abstr\">\r\n<h3 style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.2857; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BOTTOM: 7px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; COLOR: rgb(152,87,53); FONT-SIZE: 1.07em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">Abstract</h3>\r\n<h4 style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: uppercase; MARGIN: 0px 0.25em 0px 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FLOAT: left; FONT-SIZE: 1em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">BACKGROUND:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\">The aim of this study was to eval&#8205;uate the efficacy and safety of&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;in the treatment for allergic rhinitis.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: uppercase; MARGIN: 0px 0.25em 0px 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FLOAT: left; FONT-SIZE: 1em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">METHODS:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\">This study was a multicenter, randomized, parallel-controlled study. Participants were randomized to either the active&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>, sham<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>, or waitlist groups. The active and sham&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;groups received&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;treatment three times per week for 4&nbsp;weeks. In the sham group, minimal&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;at nonacupuncture points was used. The waitlist group did not receive any&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;treatment.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: uppercase; MARGIN: 0px 0.25em 0px 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FLOAT: left; FONT-SIZE: 1em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">RESULTS:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\">Of the 238 participants, 97, 94, and 47 individuals were assigned to the active&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>, sham&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>, and waitlist group, respectively. After the treatment, the difference in the total nasal symptom score (TNSS) was significantly reduced in the active&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;group compared with the sham&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;(difference: -1.03, 95% confidence interval [CI]: -1.96, -0.09, P&nbsp;=&nbsp;0.03) and waitlist (difference: -2.49, 95% CI: -3.68, -1.29, P&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;0.0001). The active&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;group exhibited a significant change in the total non-nasal symptom score (TNNSS) compared with the waitlist (difference: -0.78, 95% CI: -1.22, -0.34, P&nbsp;=&nbsp;0.0002), but not the sham&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;group (difference; 0.15, 95% CI: -0.21, 0.5, P&nbsp;=&nbsp;0.56). Both active and sham&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;treatments resulted in significant improvements in TNSS and TNNSS compared to baseline.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: uppercase; MARGIN: 0px 0.25em 0px 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FLOAT: left; FONT-SIZE: 1em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">CONCLUSION:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\"><strong><u>Active&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;showed a significantly greater effect on symptoms of allergic rhinitis than either sham&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;or no active treatment.</u></strong> The symptoms of allergic rhinitis decreased significantly after treatment in the both&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;and sham&nbsp;<span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">acupuncture</span>&nbsp;groups. <span style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px\" class=\"highlight\">Acupuncture</span>&nbsp;appears to be an effective and safe treatment for allergic rhinitis.</p>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\">ⓒ 2012 John Wiley &amp; Sons A/S. Published by Blackwell Publishing Ltd.</p>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121222_118/isuhani_1356140550722z2lIG_JPEG/%C1%F8%B7%E1.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"304\" height=\"203\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 304px; rheight: 203px\" id=\"20121222_118/isuhani_1356140550722z2lIG_JPEG/%C1%F8%B7%E1.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5BC74D7')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121222_118/isuhani_1356140550722z2lIG_JPEG/%C1%F8%B7%E1.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0.5em; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; BORDER-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT: 0px\">&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
